OL,3,CFinance Minister says #17m home
OL,4,Cheating oil support 'extremely
OL,5,Cdisappointing'
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister has announced over
OL,8,F#50million in support for households
OL,9,Fas oil prices continue to rise due to
OL,10,Fthe war in Iran.JThe Executive will
OL,11,Freceive #17million of that funding.
OL,13,FFinance Minister John O'Dowd has
OL,14,Fdescribed it as "extremely
OL,15,Fdisappointing."
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland is particularly
OL,18,Fvulnerable to the increasing costs, as
OL,19,Falmost two-thirds of households use
OL,20,Fhome heating oil.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
