OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773765954
OL,3,CFinance Minister says #17m home
OL,4,Cheating oil support 'extremely
OL,5,Cdisappointing'
OL,7,FOn Monday Sir Keir Starmer confirmed
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland will receive
OL,9,F#17million share of a #53million
OL,10,Fpackage in support for heating oil
OL,11,Fcosts that have risen due to the war
OL,12,Fin the Middle East.
OL,14,FMr O'Dowd claimed the #17million
OL,15,Ffunding would only equate to #35 per
OL,16,Fhousehold using home heating oil in
OL,17,Fthe region and said payments should
OL,18,Ftarget "those on the lowest incomes."
OL,26,@zD@HOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
