OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773765954
OL,3,CFinance Minister says #17m home
OL,4,Cheating oil support 'extremely
OL,5,Cdisappointing'
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister made the
OL,8,Fannouncement on Monday after
OL,9,FChancellor Rachel Reeves said Treasury
OL,10,Fofficials had "found the money" to
OL,11,Fhelp the 1.5 million households
OL,12,Frelying on the fuel.
OL,14,FAround two-thirds of homes in Northern
OL,15,FIreland use home heating oil compared
OL,16,Fwith the UK average of just more than
OL,17,F5%.
OL,26,@rD@OOUrD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
