FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773765954
OL,3,CFinance Minister says #17m home
OL,4,Cheating oil support 'extremely
OL,5,Cdisappointing'
OL,7,FMr O'Dowd said "it's extremely
OL,8,Fdisappointing in terms of the quantum
OL,9,Fof funding that has been made
OL,10,Favailable to the Executive".
OL,12,F"There's around half a million homes
OL,13,Fhere rely on oil-fired central heating
OL,14,Fand the Executive has been awarded
OL,15,F#17.2million from the Prime Minister's
OL,16,Fannouncement," he said.
OL,18,F"That equates to around #35 per
OL,19,Fhousehold and on that basis I think
OL,20,Fit's only right and proper that we
OL,21,Ftarget those on the lowest incomes."
OL,26,@oD@POUrD@[O]tD@AOUxD@NO]zD@AOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
