FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773765954
OL,3,CFinance Minister says #17m home
OL,4,Cheating oil support 'extremely
OL,5,Cdisappointing'
OL,7,FMr O'Dowd said that on the outbreak of
OL,8,Fthe war in Ukraine in 2022 "there was
OL,9,Fa much better financial package
OL,10,Fbrought forward than has been brought
OL,11,Fforward today, so if the economy is in
OL,12,Fa better state, then the funding
OL,13,Fcoming forward should match that".
OL,15,FHe added: "The funding package, it is
OL,16,Fbelow par, significantly below par,
OL,17,Fthere's a need for proper funding to
OL,18,Fbe brought forward.
OL,26,@pD@\OUuD@aO]wD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
