CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773765954
OL,3,CFinance Minister says #17m home
OL,4,Cheating oil support 'extremely
OL,5,Cdisappointing'
OL,7,F"It's left us in a position where we
OL,8,Fcan only now help those on the lowest
OL,9,Fincomes.
OL,11,F"Many, many workers and families out
OL,12,Fthere are struggling, we need a proper
OL,13,Fpackage to support everyone moving
OL,14,Fforward."
